  "markdown": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\">\n\n<!-- (C)2005-2007, airframes.org  - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -->\n\n<body>\n<div id=\"container\">\n\n<div id=\"top\">\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"no\">\n  <tbody><tr>\n    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"no\">\n      <a href=\"http://www.airframes.org/\"><img src=\"https://www.airframes.org/images/airframes.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"60\" border=\"0\" alt=\"airframes\"></a>\n    </td>\n\n    <td width=\"2\" class=\"no\"><a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/special99/\"><img src=\"https://www.airframes.org/images/airpx1.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\" \" width=\"1\" height=\"1\"></a>    </td>\n\n    <td width=\"470\" valign=\"top\" align=\"right\" class=\"no\">\n          </td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<hr size=\"1\" align=\"left\">\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"leftnav\">\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/\"><strong>Airframes.org</strong></a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/\">Aircraft </a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/airlines/\">Airlines</a> <br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/information.php\">Information</a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/files/\">Files</a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/resources.php\">Resources</a> <br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/addinfo.php\">About this DB</a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/new.php\">News</a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/faq.php\">FAQ</a> <br>\n<a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/supporters.php\">Supporters</a> <br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.airframes.org/login\"><b>login</b></a><br><br>\n<br>\n\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"content\">\n\n<h1>Aircraft Registration Database Lookup</h1>\n\n<p class=\"small\">Passenger airliners, cargo airplanes, business jets, helicopters, private aircraft, civil and military, \nshowing common registry data as well as mode-S radar transponder addresses.\nThe database is still <strong>under development and construction.</strong></p>\n\n  <form method=\"post\" action=\"https://www.airframes.org/\">\n    <fieldset>\n      <legend> Aircraft database &nbsp; </legend>\n      <table width=\"100%\" class=\"no\">\n        <tbody><tr><td class=\"no\">Registration:   </td><td class=\"no\"><input type=\"text\" name=\"reg1\" value=\"\"> </td><td class=\"no small\">[e.g. D-AIXA or daixa]</td><td class=\"no\" rowspan=\"4\">&nbsp;</td>\n          <td class=\"no\" align=\"right\" width=\"10%\" rowspan=\"4\">\n &nbsp; </td></tr>        \n        <tr><td class=\"no\">Selcal:         </td><td class=\"no\"><input type=\"Text\" name=\"selcal\" value=\"\"> </td><td class=\"no small\">[e.g. AS-DR or asdr]</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"no\">ICAO24 address: </td><td class=\"no\"><input type=\"Text\" name=\"ica024\" value=\"\"> </td><td class=\"no small\">[Mode-S address, default hex, or <input type=\"radio\" name=\"t\" value=\"D\">dec <input type=\"radio\" name=\"t\" value=\"O\">oct <input type=\"radio\" name=\"t\" value=\"B\">bin]</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"no\">&nbsp;          </td><td class=\"no\"><input type=\"submit\" name=\"submit\" value=\"submit\"> <input type=\"reset\" name=\"reset\" value=\"reset\"> &nbsp; </td><td class=\"no small\">... <a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/nobots.php\">no bots</a> ... &nbsp; </td></tr>\n      </tbody></table>\n    </fieldset>\n  </form>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"small\"> Your query for aircraft registration XYZZYPLUGH98. Result:  0 rows.</p><p>-- No data found on this query.</p>\n<p>No aircraft found in the database matching your query, but you have aircraft data you would expect here?<br>\nPlease, take a few seconds to <a href=\"https://www.airframes.org/amend.php\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>add a record</b></a>.</p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -->\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n</body></html>",
